data.title: TV Schedule for WUPA Atlanta, GA
data.meta_description: Check out today's TV schedule for WUPA Atlanta, GA and take a look at what is scheduled for the next 2 weeks.
data.text:
Bob's Burgers It Snakes a Village

When the Belchers visit Linda's parents in Florida, they find that the senior home where they live is full of swingers; Tina, Gene and Louise search for a legendary snake.

Bob's Burgers Family Fracas

Car trouble causes the Belchers to cancel their night out; the family hits a winning streak while competing on a TV game show.

Pawn Stars Coolest Collectibles

Revisit some of the Coolest Collectibles; a $40,000 Elvis worn Super-fly Coat, a huge collection of Star Trek memorabilia, the first ever Playboy magazine featuring Marilyn Monroe.

Pawn Stars Greatest Gambles

A look at the greatest gambles in the shop's history; an antique White Eagle medallion; a book that might be signed by Shoeless Joe Jackson; a questionable Gibson mandolin and more.

In Touch With Dr. Charles Stanley New

Dr Charles Stanley, pastor of the First Baptist Church in Atlanta, shares his insights on Christian faith and enlightens viewers with spiritual motivation.

Jerry Springer Online Feuds IRL

Stripper Meagan says she has proof that her man is a cheater; a wife and mother wants to take her online hookup with Yarial to the next level.

Creflo Dollar

Dr. Creflo Dollar ministers to people from all backgrounds with hopes for change; Creflo helps viewers find ways to renew their faith, mind, and spirit; Creflo and his wife Taffi share their vision for everyone to understand God's love and promises.

Scene of the Crime Unto Death Do Us Part

Top Secret Files: Declassified

Investigating some of the government's most infamous mysteries using interviews, reenactments, archival footage and access to years of top secret FBI files.

The Drew Barrymore Show Queen Latifah

Queen Latifah ("Living Single," "The Equalizer") plays a special round of Final Five with questions from former co-star Erika Alexander.

People Puzzler The Power of Reading

Three contestants put their pop culture knowledge to the test to complete crosswords based on the iconic puzzles in People magazine.

People Puzzler Seeking Fame & Fortune

Three contestants put their pop culture knowledge to the test to complete crosswords based on the iconic puzzles in People magazine.

Lauren Lake's Paternity Court Smith vs. Brooks

A Virginia woman thought her son's potential father died in Hurricane Katrina, but he's alive and well and still denies paternity of her 24-year-old son.

Lauren Lake's Paternity Court Weir vs. Wilson

A Tennessee woman asked her gay best friend to be her son's godfather, but now she's accusing him of getting her pregnant.

America's Court With Judge Ross Ultimate Frisbee Failure

An athlete says his rival broke his ribs during a league match.

America's Court With Judge Ross Glamping With Bears & Divorce Party Premium

A man seeks a refund after his glamping getaway wasn't as luxurious as advertised; a dispute between cousins over a loan that wasn't used as intended.

Judge Mathis

The plaintiff suspects that the defendant may be her biological granddaughter, so she has petitioned the court for a DNA test to find out the truth.

Cutlers Court Brogdon vs. Jenkins

Benjamin petitions for a paternity test after his girlfriend, Kenetha, told him during an argument that he is not the father.

Cutlers Court Goodman vs. McDonnell

John must answer for his severe smoking addiction after his girlfriend, Debbie, issues him an ultimatum.

Couples Court With the Cutlers Gordon vs. Gordon

After an Ohio woman disappeared for the weekend after a fight with her husband, the court brings in a forensic voice analyst to determine if she had an affair.

Couples Court With the Cutlers Womack vs. Bass

A Mississippi woman accuses her boyfriend's family member of leading him into the arms of other women, and he puts their engagement on hold because her lack of trust undermines their relationship.

Judge Mathis

The plaintiff says that after he broke up with the defendant she found him with another woman and destroyed his apartment in anger; he is suing for restitution.

Cutlers Court Kemper vs. Coleman

After multiple incidences of cheating resulted in a breakup, Aamonie accuses ex-girlfriend Averiona of stealing her pet dog.
